# AI-Assisted Restaurant Ordering System

A Python-based desktop application that simulates a restaurant ordering process
with an AI-assisted product recommendation feature.

## Overview
The system analyzes historical order patterns and suggests complementary items
using item-to-item association logic.

## Technologies
- Python
- Tkinter
- Basic AI (co-occurrence based recommendation)

## Features
- Interactive GUI
- Dynamic price calculation
- AI-based product suggestions

## Run
```bash
python main.py
